## ROLLBACK PROCEDURES

If critical issues found:

### Option 1: Revert Specific Commit
```bash
git revert <commit-hash>
git push origin main
```

### Option 2: Restore from Previous Branch
```bash
git checkout main~1
npm install
npm run build
```

### Option 3: Selective Rollback
- Revert only affected services
- Keep src/ folder structure
- Restore BackendService temporarily

